{"lemma":"سُخْرَةٍ","slug":"سُخْرَةٍ","root":"س.خ.ر","root_slug":"س-خ-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-خ-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19194","n19195","n19196"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"corvee"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"laughingstock"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"ridiculer"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19194","headword_ar":"سخّرهُ","root":"sxr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasoxiyrN","text_ar":"تَسْخِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He constrained him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compelled him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K,) namely, a servant, or a beast,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do what he"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to work, without recompense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wages,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and without price;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsx~rhu","text_ar":"تسخّرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, * K:) and [in like manner,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxarahu","text_ar":"سَخَرَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sixoriY~N","text_ar":"سِخْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxoriY~N","text_ar":"سُخْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he constrained him to do what he did not desire; compelled him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sx~rhu","text_ar":"سخّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made use of him without compensation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlEamali","text_ar":"فِى العَمَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in work"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasax~arotu","text_ar":"تَسَخَّرْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAb~apF lifulaAnK","text_ar":"دَابَّةً لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I rode a beast belonging to such a one without recompense."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought him under,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into subjection; rendered him subservient, submissive, tractable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manageable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sx~r A@ll~`hu AlA_ibila","text_ar":"سخّر ا@للّٰهُ الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God hath made the camels subservient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submissive, and manageable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And in the Kur [xiv. 37], it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasax~ara lakumu A@l$~amosa waA@loqamara","text_ar":"وَسَخَّرَ لَكُمُ ا@لشَّمْسَ وَا@لْقَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And He hath made subservient to you,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submissive for you, the sun and the moon"},{"kind":"text","text":"[to run their appointed courses]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sux~ira lahu","text_ar":"سُخِّرَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lh","text_ar":"له"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tusux~ira","text_ar":"تُسُخِّرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was rendered submissive"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manageable"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"practicable, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed for him agreeably with his desire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sx~r A@ll~`hu Als~afiynapa","text_ar":"سخّر ا@للّٰهُ السَّفِينَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasoxiyrN","text_ar":"تَسْخِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God made the ship to obey and to run its course; to have a good wind and voyage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sax~arahaA","text_ar":"سَخَّرَهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohimo","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur lxix. 7, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sent it upon them by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, the wind: (Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it to prevail against them by his power."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","K","TA","A","Msb","Jel"]},{"entry_id":"n19195","headword_ar":"سُخْرَةٌ","root":"sxr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who is mocked at, scoffed at, laughed at, derided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ridiculed; a laughingstock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sixoriY~N","text_ar":"سِخْرِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxoriY~N","text_ar":"سُخْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Az, A;) which are used as sing., as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~axa*uwhu","text_ar":"اِتَّخَذُوهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suiHoriy~FA","text_ar":"سُِحْرِيًّا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they made him a laughingstock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) and as pl., as in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo laka suixoriY~N","text_ar":"هُمْ لَكَ سُِخْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suixoriy~apN","text_ar":"سُِخْرِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the former being masc. and the latter fem.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they are to thee laughingstocks;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the former occurring in the Kur [see xxiii. 112, and xxxviii. 63, and xliii. 31,] with damm and with kesr accord. to different readings. (Az, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who is constrained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compelled, to do what he does not desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to work, without recompense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wages;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, * Mgh, * Msb, * K, * TA;) applied to a servant, (JK, S, Msb,) and to a beast; (JK, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxoriY~N","text_ar":"سُخْرِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sixoriY~N","text_ar":"سِخْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K) or the former of these, only, is used in this sense; and the latter, and sometimes the former also, in the sense immediately preceding: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxorapN","text_ar":"سُخْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as a pl., (JK, A,) as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`w^ulaA='i suxorapN lils~uloTaAni","text_ar":"هٰوُلَا=ءِ سُخْرَةٌ لِلسُّلْطَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"these are persons made use of without compensation for the Sultán:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * A:) it also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who employs any person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he has subjected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compelled to obey him, without recompense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wages:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [or this is a mistake, and the correct signification is]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who is so employed by him who has subjected him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-  It is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasoxiyrN","text_ar":"تَسْخِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 2]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"smE","text_ar":"سمع"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Msb","K","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n19196","headword_ar":"سُخَرَةٌ","root":"sxr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who mocks at, scoffs at, laughs at, derides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ridicules, others,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoxarapN","text_ar":"مَسْخَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}